products.title: Seagate FireCuda 120 SSD 2TB Internal Solid State Drive – SATA 6Gb/s 3D TLC for Gaming PC Laptop (ZA2000GM10001)
features: HIGH CAPACITY Up to 2TB of capacity means accumulating games and content without fear of maxing out space.
MAXIMUM SPEED Get maxed out SATA 6Gb/s speeds of 560/540 MB/s (sequential read/write).
PLUG AND PLAY With a compatible SATA 6Gb/s interface, install or upgrade a SSD in minutes.
LONG-TERM ENDURANCE Game confidently a 5-year limited and the durability 1. 8M hours mean time between failures (MTBF), plus 3-year Rescue Service
PERFORMANCE MONITORING Use SeaTools SSD to test and analyze this fast flash drive.
products.description: Built for speed and durability, the highly-adaptable FireCuda 120 takes on the rigors of PC gaming. Thanks to maxed out SATA 6Gb/s SSD speeds of up to 560/540 MB/s (sequential read/write), loading will no longer be a waste of time. And with the durability of up to 5600TB TBW (total bytes written), it plugs in and plays for a long time. From adding a new boot drive to boosting a battlestation’s capacity, get ready to play with FireCuda 120.
